\Longleftrightarrow \dfrac{x^4_{1}x^2_{2}x^2_{3}}{(ax_{1}+\ln{x_{1}})(ax_{2}+\ln{x_{2}})(ax_{3}+\ln{x_{3}})}=x^2_{1}\cdot x_{2}\cdot x_{3}
